            .text = "What kind of tone will you attempt to set in your campaign this fall?",
            .answers = .{
                .{
                    .text = "I will campaign as a mainstream liberal Democrat, emphasizing key parts of our platform and pressing the case for more vigilance in our national defense.",
                    .feedback = "This is the party line that people want to hear. Good luck this fall!",
