                .{
                    .text = "I am supportive of a civil rights bill and will work with Congress to get one written and passed.",
                },
                .{
                    .text = "This is something that is more appropriately addressed by individual states, though I will do anything I can to enforce the decisions of our Supreme Court.",
                },
                .{
                    .text = "I would not support a measure like this. This would be an unnecessary and unconstitutional interference into the rights of our states.",
                },
            },
        },
        .{
            .text = "Do you believe that Cuba has been lost to the Communists as of this time? If so, do you think it is partially the fault of the United States?",
            .answers = .{
                .{
                    .text = "We've seen some alarming things out of Cuba, but this isn't necessarily a lost cause. Cuba has not declared itself a Communist state and we should be making overtures to prevent that.",
                },
                .{
                    .text = "We will defend our base at Guantanamo and do anything else that is necessary if Cuba continues its hostility. However, it is too early to make a conclusive determination at this point.",
                },
                .{
                    .text = "What we've unfortunately seen in Cuba is the consequence of insufficient support for anti-Communist governments and movements. We need to be much more aggressive in our actions against the Castro government.",
                    .feedback = "It's good to be aggressive during the campaign, but can you back it up if you are elected?",
                },
            },
        },
        .{
            .text = "Do you support a minimum wage of $1.25 per hour, with some exceptions for small business? Such a measure was recently defeated in Congress.",
            .answers = .{
                .{
                    .text = "I support this measure, and believe it would be greatly beneficial to millions of American workers.",
