        .{
            .text = "How serious, at the current time, do you believe the internal Communist threat is?",
            .answers = .{
                .{
                    .text = "The last thing we need is a return to excesses and witch-hunts of the early 1950s. We need to keep ourselves focused on the external Communist threat.",
